 / subscription.All the registered labourers must possess an identity card in which registration fees and subscription amount is mentioned.Moreover, there must be a certified and completed identity certification in which subscription amount is mentioned, is to be attached.Auzaar (Tool Kit) Kharidne Hetu Updaan EligibilityAll the candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as mentioned in the table below:-Eligibility Criteria / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093eMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e1Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoBuilding and Construction Workers (BOCW) can take this scheme benefits to get assisted in their work.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}